HEADWORD: Notidanian
<hw>No`ti*da"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ back +
<?/ comely.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of several species of
sharks of the family <fam>Notidanidae</fam>, or <fam>Hexanchidae</fam>.
Called also <altname>cow sharks</altname>. See <er>Shark</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
